title: Arbor Skateboards :: KJ Nakanelua - Raw Run
description:
New to the team, KJ Nakanelua, shows us a ballsy island style version of skating a California Classic. From hand stands and shakas to speed wobbles and big slides, this video has it all..

Don't forget to 'breathe in the air' and enjoy!!

Follow Cam/Edit: Nate Shute
Rider: KJ Nakanelua

To learn more about Arbor Skateboards visit: arborcollective.com/skateboards
